FLSmidth Group CEO, Thomas Schulz, speaks about the expanded facilities at its Delmas Supercenter in South Africa. He explains  how it will contribute to the group’s productivity and customer service while improving stock availability and lead times. The group has a total of six Supercenters globally. “The expansion in South Africa is aligned with our corporate mission to provide sustainable productivity enhancements for our customers,” says  Stephan Kruger, FLSmidth Director for Manufacturing and Warehousing . “It raises our engineering capability to support local customers, while also improving our efficiencies to compete globally in certain lines of products.” Read the details and highlights of the supercenter here